Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:06.55,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's something fascinating about stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:08.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}be they criminals or actors!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.68,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A big case at a magician's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:13.12,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan and Heiji figure out the tricks and gimmicks behind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:14.66,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:16.32,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:18.22,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:45.28,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}At the famous magician Dōgo Hoshikawa's show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:49.78,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}we were invited to the home of the legendary magician, Mr Masakage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:56.59,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That day was the 10th anniversary of Mr Masakage's disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:53.98,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Dōgo Hoshikawa (27)\NMagician
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:53.98,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Riki Handa (41)\NMagician
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The magician's disciples had all gathered there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we're really going to do a show together, my grand finale will be the "resurrection of the witch"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:08.68,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tenko Himemiya (32)\NMagician
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A huge cross will be placed in the middle of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be tied to the cross, with volunteers from the audience holding the ropes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My assistants will set fire to the cross, but I'll disappear before it burns away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll rise miraculously from the ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the light's burnt out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:02:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's bleedin' from her head and won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it. Her body's already cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's been dead for more than 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you two find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but Hoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was with us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.94,0:03:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's in the next room callin' for an ambulance an' cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hattori. Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The window's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the killer jumped out an' landed in the bushes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they could get away through the back gate no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji, c'mere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check out the room next to the one where we found Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a library of reference works on magic that Mr. Masakage{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} gathered from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did ya keep any valuables in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... It's mostly books and magazine clippings, nothing too rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We used to flip through them all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:29.01,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mari Masakage (54)\NMr. Masakage's Wife
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The intruder was looking for the forbidden notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband wrote down the secrets to all his original illusions in a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't even let me read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He called it "The Masakage Notes".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Masakage Notes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? If it isn't Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did {\i1}you{\i0} get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm on summer break. I came to Tokyo to catch a magic show
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:05:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'cause some stupid girl wanted an "enchanted experience".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who're ya callin' stupid, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way you pop up at all these crime scenes has to be black magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why are you {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We met these three magicians after the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They invited us to their master's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then one of 'em got killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a magician too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenko Imemiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's pretty famous overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were just talking about doing a show together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who found the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me and the two girls behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went looking for Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to call her for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should she'd be here in the master's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't see anything at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:06:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was dark, and when I tried to turn on the lights, we had a blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then when the lights went back on,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we saw Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body at the end of the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer darkened the hallway by loosenin' the light bulbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only lights that went out were the ones in that hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was set so if somebody tried to switch the lights on, they'd trigger a blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This switch's been tampered with to cause a short circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The library next to the body contained a valuable notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it ain't got no windows or exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:38.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the window in the master's room next door is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the murderer must've stole the notebook an' escaped out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{そうや...停電したら、一階にあるブレーカー上げに行かなアカンやろ？}Speakin' of which, if there was a blackout, wouldn't you need to go flip the breaker on the first floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:07:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thief planned to use that moment to escape through the window in the master's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the heist didn't work as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally this lady is the only person in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But today she had seven guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} entered the library without turnin' the blackout switch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She saw the thief's face, so he had to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the thief was lookin' for the notebook in a panic,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha an' the others came lookin' for Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time the blackout trick worked, so the murderer dumped the body in the hall an' ran for the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everybody was so shocked by the stiff, they didn't see the killer escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only possible conclusion is that this was the work of an intruder who broke in to steal the magician's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...the real killer was Hoshikawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the guy who flipped the blackout switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Durin' the blackout, there was more than enough time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for you to move Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body, which you'd hidden in the library beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,an' come back to Kazuha and Ran before the lights turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.{??}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These two girls were hugging me tight the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hugging?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Why"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Cause it was dark an' creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you clung to this jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was holdin' on to him like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I was holding Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? He couldn't have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is just like that case with Araide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ya big dope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just a blackout!\NActin' like a little baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}! She can't help it, she's just a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where were you two during the blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:14.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was taking a nap downstairs, in the room below the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd just gone in to wake Handa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} up when the blackout happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three have solid alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the work of a burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what's this valuable notebook I keep hearing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Masakage Notes. It's a collection of all the original illusions invented by my husband, Mr. Masakage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Masakage? I used to watch him on TV when I was a lad!{un-UK this}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His illusions were amazing, and he and his lovely assistant worked so perfectly together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard about them too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never forgot them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was that assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:10:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Is that so? But where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I remember hearing that he went missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was ten years ago on this very day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He often went off on trips without telling me, so I wasn't worried at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then six months passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dogo, Riki and Tenko, who were all living here, moved out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and started their own careers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, ten years later, we're back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you're the one who invited everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk about the three of us doing a show together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I come here every year, on the anniversary of the master's disappearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:42.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to eat Mrs. Masakage's cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know of anyone who had a grudge against Mr. Masakage{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}? A jealous rival, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If what Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said is true, the murderer knew Mrs. Masakage lived alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and also knew the layout of the house by heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With Mr. Masakage gone, his book of tricks would be worth a lot of money to the right person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone who used to visit this house and might want to exploit him like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Masakage{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} wasn't the kind of person who made enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there was one man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came by several times, saying that he wanted to meet my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he was a fan, so finally I invited him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But as soon as he got to my husband's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:35.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come out, you petty, thieving trickster who stole my act!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was shouting like mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've told you about this, haven't I, Handa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was over five years ago, so I don't recall him clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:53.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But around that time, things around the house seemed to have moved slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then again, maybe I imagined it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think something in the room changed before and after we found the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so too, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You noticed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can't quite remember what was off...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should call Shin'ichi and ask him about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought he wouldn't give you his number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He finally told me the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:26.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shoot! I haven't turned my cell phone off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don'tcha call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s such a smart guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you tell him about the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he can solve it... in... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm gonna hang on to this phone 'til {\i1}I{\i0} close the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!{Conan, Heiji, hang on}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, smart guy? What brilliant theory have ya got?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it, eh, Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:56.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just solved the whole case a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's some detail buggin' ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like how the thief happened to choose this particular day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. Today's the anniversary of Mr. Masakage's disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the murderer was a thief who'd been casing the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they should've known this was a special day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that Mrs. Masakage wasn't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An' it's funny there ain't no blood at the spot where Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was bludgeoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If things happened the way I deduced, she shoulda been attacked in the hallway or the library,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I don't see a trace of blood there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:34.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder site's too clean for this to be anything other than a premeditated crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was just a thief, we'd find blood in the floor tiles or wood grain or somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An' third...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dunno why, but she's been buggin' me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't concentrate on my detective work when I see her all flirtin' an' smilin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By any chance, do "flirting" and "smiling"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,come before the phrase "with other guys", or "trying to date other guys"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! That's it! You got it, Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:46.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it, Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no... I mean, could-uh— could go for a fresh drink.{Best I could think of.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{VIU: That dude on TV said}I saw on TV that the temperature\Nwent up to 39 degrees yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was hot, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:15:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. I remember seein' it on the news at the airport this mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? Ya got any idea what's up, Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...such a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that s'pposed to mean?! Who ya callin a kid, short stack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whaddya thinkin', losin' it at a little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poor Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poor Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} my arse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brat's sayin' stupid stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:37.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who's being stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What can you recall about the suspicious man who visited you five years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apart from your husband's students here, did any other magicians visit this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before my husband vanished ten years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he often had guests,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I didn't know them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband designed this house,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and sometimes he'd invite people over just to show it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He designed the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had magic tricks that could only be performed here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and many guests came to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially the Christmas tree trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was very popular. It always got a big cheer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, nothing, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That had nothing to do with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of trick was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only Mr. Masakage can tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now that he's gone missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's no way to know how his illusions were done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us more about the suspicious man who came to visit you five years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:17:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was a rival magician who thought your husband, Mr. Masakage, had stolen his tricks,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he was probably looking for the Masakage Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If somebody broke into this house
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the intention of getting the notebook in the library,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but had to kill Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to silence her when she caught him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he's sure to be the man from five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you remember anything about him? Height, facial features, anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about race? Was he Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He spoke fluent Japanese and had dark hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he was wearing a hat, so I didn't see his hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't see his eyes, since he was wearing sunglasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his face was hidden behind a beard.{POSSIBLY A MISTRANSLATION}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he was slightly taller than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hat, sunglasses and facial hair, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could've been a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, did you check to see if the Masakage Notes have been stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know where he kept the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,except that it was in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For all we know, he took it with him ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, ya got any photo albums?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Photo albums?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With all those guests and parties, you must've taken pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a photo of the guy from five years ago in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are your photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In my husband's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why does the door get stuck in the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:19:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband designed it that way so he could have larger rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:02.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess the master's talents didn't extend to architecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're ya two doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See anyone who looks like that man from five years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure have a lot of photo albums.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heiji! There's no way we're gonna find the guy in these photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, duh! That ain't what we're lookin' for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This must be the famous Christmas tree trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the tree was placed at the end of the hall where we found Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we're on to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:19:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha! Take a look at this, Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:19:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's those three when they were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ya know what this could mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's something suspicious about that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That thing on the ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a screen for a projector!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks normal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you usually hang a screen from a wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need room to sit and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's not the case here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, it's really far from the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you say it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's no ordinary screen, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has a slit so people can walk through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:56.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen a magic trick where real people seem to walk right out of a movie screen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We used to rehearse magic tricks in here. That's why it's not close to a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's really nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back in the day, we'd all gather here and practise together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:14.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now, you're all fantastic magicians, and no longer have use for this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to the master and this room that we're as good as we are today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's always a trick behind magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why practising is so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want your audience to not see through the trick, you must practise it over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the screen has a hole in it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, we used to come to this room every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband needed to make sure the timing was right
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and no strange shadows would appear on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! The shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The shadow of the vase was different!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of the vase?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:22:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first time we were in the hall, the moonlight was shining on the vase from behind, throwing it in shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we found Tenko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body after the blackout,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the moonlight was shining on the vase from the side!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The patterns on it were clear as day!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...? The moon don't move that fast, dummies!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.44,0:22:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of the vase...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: "Conan & Heiji's Deduction Magic (The Resolution)"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.04,0:24:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:23.51,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, we'll solve the case\Nwith our famous comedy act!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.51,0:24:26.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do, make me laugh?\NIt's a combo, it's a combo!
